# All products block

A reusable theme block that displays all products from a merchant-selected collection in a sortable grid. Designed for small catalogs (~10 products max), with no pagination or infinite scroll needed.

## Product source

- Merchant selects a **collection** as the product source via the theme editor
- Renders using the **existing product card** block from the theme (to be adjusted separately later)

## Sorting

- Client-side sorting with **no page reload**
- Sort options displayed at the top of the block
- Each sort option can be individually **toggled on/off** in the theme editor
- Merchant can set the **default sort option**

### Available sort options

| Option | Direction   |
| ------ | ----------- |
| Price  | Low to high |
| Price  | High to low |
| Name   | A to Z      |
| Name   | Z to A      |

## Grid layout

- Products displayed in a **CSS grid**
- Defaults: **4 columns** desktop, **2 columns** mobile
- Column and row gaps are configurable

## Theme editor settings

### Content

- `collection` — collection picker (product source)

### Sorting

- `default_sort` — select (default sort option shown on load)
- `show_sort_price_asc` — checkbox (show "Price: low to high", default: true)
- `show_sort_price_desc` — checkbox (show "Price: high to low", default: true)
- `show_sort_name_asc` — checkbox (show "Name: A to Z", default: true)
- `show_sort_name_desc` — checkbox (show "Name: Z to A", default: true)

### Grid

- `columns` — range 1–8, default 4 (desktop)
- `mobile_columns` — select 1 or 2, default 2
- `columns_gap` — range 0–100px, default 8px
- `rows_gap` — range 0–100px, default 8px

### Section layout

- `section_width` — select `page-width` or `full-width`
- `color_scheme` — color scheme picker
- `padding-block-start` — range 0–100px, default 48px
- `padding-block-end` — range 0–100px, default 48px
